narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: This course helped very much. I have gained many translation tools, knowledges, and method, which makes me never be afraid of translating. I gained study method as well. This is my first semester at Yale graduate school, I did not even know how to prepare for graduate class. This course helped mw with that and offered me long-term method for study.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Nothing needed. To me, it was really great because I learned a lot.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would recommend this course to anyone who interested in China and Chinese history. This is a course with helpful method any sinologist will need.
